---
layout: layout-base.njk
title: RadioPeng
---

<section class="hero hero-bold">
  <div class="hero-kicker">Independent freeform radio</div>
  <h1>Signal acquired.</h1>
  <p>
    RadioPeng broadcasts strange, beautiful, occasionally unwise music.
    Press play. Drift responsibly.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-tags" aria-label="Station traits">
    <span>Human curated</span>
    <span>No algorithm playlists</span>
    <span>Broadcasting live</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="grid">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Latest Articles</h2>

    <div class="article-list">
      {% set posts = collections.articles | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts.slice(0,5) %}
        <a class="article" href="{{ post.url }}">
          <div class="kicker">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
          <div class="name">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <div class="blurb">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card stream-card">
    <h2>The Stream</h2>
    <p class="meta">
      Live audio stream served via AzuraCast.<br/>
      Minimal UI. No nonsense.
    </p>
    <div class="stream-actions">
      <button class="btn stream-cta" id="playBtnHome" type="button">Play Live</button>
      <a class="stream-manifesto" href="/manifesto/">Read the manifesto →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
